{"tid":1703004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科大下週一將會停課","createTime":"2019-11-10T05:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:34:12.000Z","uid":104138,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41fd42cfb16a3cd5893ec512ff946affe1cdcda5","tid":1703004,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"[科大振翅新聞] 科大下週一停課<br />\n<br />\n校方表示為了預留足夠時間修葺校園，決定取消下週一(十一月十一日)所有課堂與官方活動。 <br />\n<br />\n大學的所有辦公室，圖書館和室內體育設施將關閉。 而戶外運動設施（包括網球場、海濱室外籃球場和迷你足球場）將保持開放。 <br />\n<br />\n至於校園內餐飲服務，校園服務辦公室（CSO）將稍後以電郵通知其開放時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4S8qKx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4S8qKx.png&h=1efb1870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37862ba949443966968e23452bf4775f1f612cf3","tid":1703004,"uid":34047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推到其他大學跟"},{"pid":"81d8b96eb0eea5a9234e9fd82fdce87ff0448e0e","tid":1703004,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04f7f3860c37034982fbf4465f24952af1e64d5","tid":1703004,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"要一齊令1111行動成功 你而家有四樣野可以做！<br />\n<br />\n第一 推呢個post上返熱門 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n第二 幫手宣傳出去 ig/fb /WhatsApp/tg<br />\n第三 今晚幫手貼連儂牆<br />\n第四 加入返tg group <a href=\"http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=32995775\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n最後聽日7:00要見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XknsjfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h